Every year, The Future Awards Africa celebrates young Africans between the ages of 18 and 31, who have made outstanding achievement in the year under consideration The nomination list for this year’s event themed ‘Nigeria’s New Tribe’ was released on Sunday, November 3 by the central working committee (CWC) of the awards. The nomination list saw the nominees representing outstanding young talents, innovators, entrepreneurs, and community advocates who are breaking boundaries in various industries vying for the awards spanning 21 categories. The Future Awards 2019 is billed to hold on November 24 at the Balmoral Centre, Federal Palace Hotel, Lagos, Here is a list of the nominees for acting and music. THE FUTURE AWARDS AFRICA PRIZE FOR MUSIC Who are you voting for, let us know below: 